data.description: *** Accepting offers between $980,000-999,000 *** Welcome to your dream home in the charming community of Ramona, This stunning, newly built residence is a true gem, offering modern elegance, breathtaking views, and a serene lifestyle. Situated on a generous .7 acre lot, this home boasts ample space & privacy. The tastefully designed interior features luxurious finishes throughout. The heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, which is a culinary enthusiast's dream come true. This kitchen is as functional as it is beautiful.  The living area seamlessly flows into the relaxing rear covered patio, where you can unwind and soak in the tranquility of your surroundings. The custom pavers create an inviting outdoor space perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying a quiet evening with loved ones. The meticulously landscaped backyard is a true oasis, featuring artificial turf & vinyl fencing for low-maintenance living. Whether you're hosting a summer barbecue or lounging under the sun, this backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. Located on a quiet street, this home is nestled in a peaceful neighborhood that exudes a sense of community. The nearby schools, catering to all levels, make this an ideal location for families seeking quality education for their children. In addition to its idyllic setting, this home is conveniently located near a variety of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants, and recreational facilities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours!
